I was getting a bash for around 115 every now and then when it first came about on Test...I wasn't averaging anywhere near that, though, but I was getting higher hits than my one handers (blasphemous blade and blade of carnage).  I quickly gave up on using shields because the most effective way to use them at the time seemed to be ghetto bashing, which is extremely annoying.  I tried again a few days later for a few minutes and seemed to be hitting for far less with my shield.  Who knows, I could be hitting for 1k with a shield today...things change on Test constantly.<br>
<br>
