This is just so wrong IMO.  They are hopefully breaking the clerics role as only healer in EQ with the new healing changes.    Warriors should be the best tanks, not the only viable tanks.  Clerics should be the best healers, not only viable healer.  Right now Knights can tank just fine in many places, I think they should be able to tank in even more.  But warriors should be the choice for the hardest combats. <p><a href =http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=210569>Fraustkilicus, Halfling Paladin</a> 

